postcontent: For sale is a very nice and barely used Smith & Wesson M&P 15-22 Pistol. This has only had 50 rounds down the pipe for a function test only. This pistol takes the 10 or 25 round Smith & Wesson 15-22 magazine. I have misplaced the magazine and can not find it, therefore, this will not come with one. You will have to purchase your own magazine from somewhere else, or if you have the 15-22 rifle, then you already own a magazine to fit this pistol. This pistol will come with the factory box, paperwork, & lock. These are very rare pistols because they were discontinued a couple years ago. I have seen these go on gunbroker from $1,350 to $1,625 a piece, look up the completed auctions if you don't believe me. This is a quick way for someone to make some cash. This is an extremely fun pistol to shoot, I just don't have a place to shoot it anymore. My loss, your gain.
